291
00:13:17,119 --> 00:13:18,039
I am Gu Tiancheng.

292
00:13:23,359 --> 00:13:24,960
Actually, I know that today's occasion

293
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,719
concerns your ability to support your families.

294
00:13:29,719 --> 00:13:31,320
My actions during this period

295
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:33,400
are actually destroying the livelihoods

296
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,440
you've worked so hard to build.

297
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:38,599
Here,

298
00:13:39,799 --> 00:13:41,039
I want to apologize to everyone.

299
00:13:54,479 --> 00:13:56,599
I can't think of a better way to apologize.

300
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,799
And all I can think of

301
00:13:59,719 --> 00:14:01,400
is to stop living the way I used to,

302
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,080
and instead embed my future

303
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,679
into your future.

304
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:20,280
What you all see here

305
00:14:20,679 --> 00:14:22,880
are the previously suspended new product R&D projects.

306
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,760
And my capability

307
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,559
lies in asset investment.

308
00:14:28,119 --> 00:14:30,039
In order to get these new product development projects

309
00:14:30,719 --> 00:14:31,840
back on track,

310
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,679
I am willing to spare no effort in increasing investment.

311
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,520
Because without all of you,

312
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,280
there would be no me.

313
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,599
I know I am a bad person,

314
00:14:43,799 --> 00:14:44,760
and in the past,

315
00:14:46,239 --> 00:14:47,840
I've done many things that hurt you.

316
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,719
But since I'm already thick-skinned,

317
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,239
I will brazenly

318
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,880
ask you all one more time.

319
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,280
Can you trust me just this once?

320
00:14:59,919 --> 00:15:01,679
Can you give me, Gu Tiancheng, a chance?

321
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:04,000
Let me protect all of you.

322
00:15:05,799 --> 00:15:06,520
Please.

323
00:15:19,239 --> 00:15:19,880
President Gu,

324
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,200
please don't be nervous.

325
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:23,760
Your speech just now was excellent.

326
00:15:30,039 --> 00:15:30,719
What's the result?

327
00:15:35,559 --> 00:15:36,400
Say something!

328
00:15:37,479 --> 00:15:38,559
Don't scare me, okay?

329
00:15:43,919 --> 00:15:44,440
Come in.

330
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,559
What's the result?

331
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:48,679
Wait a minute.

332
00:15:49,559 --> 00:15:50,359
Let me prepare myself.

333
00:15:59,200 --> 00:15:59,760
Alright.

334
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,520
Tell me.

335
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:04,119
The result might not be what you expected.

336
00:16:09,280 --> 00:16:09,880
Then what is it?

337
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:11,440
The labor union announced

338
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:13,520
their support for Board Director Gu

339
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:14,320
to take over as President.

340
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:15,159
What?

341
00:16:25,280 --> 00:16:26,119
Although we only got

342
00:16:26,119 --> 00:16:27,159
half of the approval rating,

343
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,880
it's still higher than Feng Ziang's.

344
00:16:29,239 --> 00:16:29,880
Right now,

345
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:30,919
the people in the labor union

346
00:16:31,159 --> 00:16:32,159
all support you, President Gu.

347
00:16:33,679 --> 00:16:34,239
However,

348
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:35,200
this time,

349
00:16:35,599 --> 00:16:36,520
I really have to thank you.

350
00:16:36,799 --> 00:16:37,640
If it weren't for you,

351
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:38,760
we wouldn't have this result.

352
00:16:39,159 --> 00:16:40,039
It's also because of you...

353
00:16:49,520 --> 00:16:50,039
President.

354
00:16:51,119 --> 00:16:51,679
Slow down.

355
00:17:00,679 --> 00:17:02,320
Are you standing here to welcome me?

356
00:17:03,039 --> 00:17:04,800
Congratulations on becoming President.

357
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:13,479
Good morning,

358
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:15,520
Director Feng.

359
00:17:16,760 --> 00:17:18,000
Congratulations on becoming President.

360
00:17:19,479 --> 00:17:20,640
We all expect you

361
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:21,599
to lead Feimanchi

362
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:22,719
back to glory.

363
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,199
Do you really mean that?

364
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:26,439
Yes.

365
00:17:26,439 --> 00:17:27,920
From the bottom of our hearts.

366
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:30,359
To prove your sincerity,

367
00:17:31,079 --> 00:17:32,400
go upstairs for a meeting right now.

368
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:34,880
No one is allowed to be absent.

369
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:47,040
Since everyone is here,

370
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,160
let's get started.

371
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:51,560
Regarding the dismissal of Board Director Feng Ziang,

372
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,760
are there any other voting procedures needed?

373
00:18:04,959 --> 00:18:07,439
I heard your acting was quite realistic this time.

374
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,040
I'm a perfectionist.

375
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:10,199
With everything,

376
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:11,479
I make sure it's flawless.

377
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:13,680
I can't let anyone see any flaws.

378
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:17,839
But being dismissed from your position

379
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:20,079
must have been quite hard for you, right?

380
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,160
Thank you

381
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,800
for going along with our plan.

382
00:18:26,439 --> 00:18:27,439
But is it really okay?

383
00:18:28,239 --> 00:18:28,920
You had to give up

384
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:30,239
the CEO position.

385
00:18:31,280 --> 00:18:32,800
Isn't it just for a day or two?

386
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:34,439
Bide one's time.

387
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,040
I can still hold on.

388
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,880
Gu Tiancheng thinks he can rest easy now.

389
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,560
But he doesn't realize

390
00:18:43,319 --> 00:18:44,280
what is waiting

391
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:45,719
for him.

392
00:18:49,319 --> 00:18:50,199
You mean

393
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,599
you want Gu Tiancheng to become Chairman directly?

394
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:53,520
Yes.

395
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:56,119
If we stop him now,

396
00:18:57,079 --> 00:18:58,760
his competitive spirit will only grow stronger.

397
00:18:59,479 --> 00:19:01,479
Only by letting him taste a little sweetness first

398
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:03,359
will he completely relax.

399
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:07,319
You have a point.

400
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,839
If he wants to save the factory,

401
00:19:09,319 --> 00:19:11,560
he can only develop new products and projects.

402
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,959
And that will be the foundation of the company's collapse.

403
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:15,199
Nelson Gu

404
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:16,959
will also go bankrupt because of it.

405
00:19:18,079 --> 00:19:18,599
Okay.

406
00:19:18,719 --> 00:19:19,199
I'll do it.

407
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:23,760
Let him stay in the Chairman position for now

408
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:24,880
and do whatever he wants.

409
00:19:25,719 --> 00:19:26,839
Anyway, in a few days,

410
00:19:28,479 --> 00:19:29,520
he will have nothing.

411
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,239
Very good.

412
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:34,199
Cheers.

413
00:19:41,560 --> 00:19:42,280
Thanks to you.

414
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,640
I'll keep an eye on you to make sure you work hard.

415
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:48,520
Keep it up.

416
00:19:50,199 --> 00:19:50,800
I will.

417
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:20,079
Tan Feng.

418
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,239
Can you hear me?

419
00:20:23,239 --> 00:20:25,000
Nod if you can hear me.

420
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,880
Nodding is too hard for him.

421
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,280
Tan Feng.

422
00:20:30,479 --> 00:20:32,280
Can you hear Officer Lin?

423
00:20:33,119 --> 00:20:34,599
Blink if you can hear her.

424
00:20:37,520 --> 00:20:38,199
Great.

425
00:20:39,839 --> 00:20:40,359
We have a

426
00:20:40,359 --> 00:20:41,599
very important question to ask you.

427
00:20:42,359 --> 00:20:43,239
Do you know

428
00:20:43,800 --> 00:20:45,839
who the real killer of Du Zheng is?

429
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:47,640
If you know,

430
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,359
blink once.

431
00:20:53,319 --> 00:20:55,280
Do you remember his name?

432
00:21:00,199 --> 00:21:01,000
Don't go to sleep.

433
00:21:01,199 --> 00:21:01,839
Wake up.

434
00:21:04,199 --> 00:21:05,359
Are you insisting on going against me?

435
00:21:05,959 --> 00:21:06,800
Let me tell you,

436
00:21:06,880 --> 00:21:07,640
even if you act like this,

437
00:21:07,719 --> 00:21:08,520
we can still arrest you.

438
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:09,199
That's enough.

439
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:11,839
Let's stop here for today.

440
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:13,400
He's still a patient.

441
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:14,479
He needs to rest.

442
00:21:14,959 --> 00:21:15,800
I informed you,

443
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:18,160
but not for you to interrogate him right away.

444
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:20,199
Senior.

445
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:21,760
No matter what,

446
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,520
we've gained something today.

447
00:21:25,239 --> 00:21:25,839
Doctor,

448
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:27,839
when can we talk to him?

449
00:21:28,199 --> 00:21:29,400
In about three or four days.

450
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:30,560
After three or four days,

451
00:21:30,760 --> 00:21:31,800
his brain edema will disappear,

452
00:21:32,040 --> 00:21:33,680
and he'll basically be able to speak and write.

453
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:39,040
Okay.

454
00:21:39,599 --> 00:21:41,079
Please notify me as soon as possible.
